graph TB
    subgraph "Backend API Container"
        API[API Layer]
        Orch[Orchestrator]
        Agents[Agent System]
        LLM[LLM Provider]
        Memory[Memory Store]
        Quality[Quality Assurance]
        Context[Context Management]
        Infra[Infrastructure]
    end

    subgraph "Frontend UI Container"
        Dashboard[Project Dashboard]
        Workspace[Workspace Viewer]
        State[State Management]
    end

    User[Developer] --> Dashboard
    User --> Workspace

    Dashboard --> API
    Workspace --> API

    API --> Orch
    Orch --> Agents
    Agents --> LLM
    Agents --> Memory
    Agents --> Quality
    Agents --> Context
    Orch --> Infra

    State -.->|manages| Dashboard
    State -.->|manages| Workspace

    LLM -.->|API calls| CodexAPI[Codex API]
    LLM -.->|API calls| ClaudeAPI[Claude API]
    LLM -.->|API calls| GeminiAPI[Gemini API]

    Infra -.->|file I/O| FS[File System]
    Infra -.->|git ops| Git[Git CLI]